If you are running out of time to execute
your manual test cases ATOC provides you with a
platform to execute with a single click.
You can upload your test artifacts to our secured FTP
server through ATOC.
You can configure test suites from our easy-to-use web
UI.
You can choose environment to run your test cases.
Option to run test cases immediately or schedule them
to run at a later time.
ATOC reporting will provide you with a set of reports for
analysis.
ATOC is built on SOA architecture.
Secured authentication and authorization process.
Built on HTML5, JQuery and Spring, Hibernate
frame works.
Automated scripts to create VM on the cloud and
create the platform to run test cases based on
environments selected by user.
Easy to configure and build reports.
